metadata.name: MetaFantasy Pass #1
metadata.description: Welcome to the world of MetaFantasy! We have prepared a brand new fantasy experience for you. With our MetaFantasy Pass, you will gain access to unique character customization options, limited-edition equipment, and even more in-game privileges. Join our virtual world and adventure with players from all over the world, and become the strongest adventurer. Don't wait, purchase your MetaFantasy Pass now and start your adventure today!
